---
import ServicePage from '../layouts/ServicePage.astro';

const faqs = [
  {
    question: "Does ear hair waxing hurt?",
    answer: "Ear hair waxing is quick and causes minimal discomfort. The wax is applied only to the outer ear area, not inside the ear canal, making it a safe and relatively painless procedure."
  },
  {
    question: "How often should I get my ears waxed?",
    answer: "Most clients schedule ear hair waxing every 4-6 weeks, though this varies depending on how quickly your hair grows."
  },
  {
    question: "Is ear waxing safe?",
    answer: "Yes, when performed by a professional. We only wax the outer ear and never insert wax into the ear canal. This is a safe, effective way to remove unsightly ear hair."
  }
];
---

<ServicePage
  title="Ear Hair Waxing Scottsdale | Men's Ear Hair Removal"
  description="Professional ear hair waxing in Scottsdale. Safe, quick removal of unsightly ear hair. Clean, precise results for men. Book your appointment today!"
  price="$15"
  duration="5-10 min"
  location="scottsdale"
  faqs={faqs}
>

<!-- Hero Image -->
<div class="mb-8">
  <img 
    src="/images/6358773dfa2fa42351f2e029_e44d6da5-be58-48f9-b936-c001d4202df5_ear-hair-waxing.jpeg"
    alt="Ear hair waxing service at Rejuvenate You in Scottsdale"
    class="w-full h-64 md:h-80 object-cover rounded-xl"
  />
</div>

<p class="text-lg mb-6">
  Eliminate unsightly ear hair with our quick and effective ear hair waxing service. This simple treatment removes hair from the outer ear area, leaving you looking well-groomed and polished.
</p>

<h2 class="text-2xl font-bold mb-4" style="color: #7B2D8E;">Why Get Your Ears Waxed?</h2>

<div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-6 mb-8">
  <div>
    <img 
      src="/images/6358773dfa2fa42351f2e029_a57befb1-29d1-4923-acad-9f18eabea2c0_ear-hair-removal-wax.jpeg"
      alt="Ear hair removal waxing"
      class="w-full h-48 object-cover rounded-lg mb-4"
    />
  </div>
  <div class="flex flex-col justify-center">
    <p class="mb-4">
      Ear hair is a common concern for many men. While it's completely natural, removing it creates a cleaner, more polished appearance.
    </p>
    <ul class="list-disc pl-5 space-y-2 text-gray-700">
      <li>Quick and virtually painless</li>
      <li>Lasts 4-6 weeks</li>
      <li>More effective than trimming</li>
      <li>No more visible ear hair</li>
    </ul>
  </div>
</div>

<h2 class="text-2xl font-bold mb-4" style="color: #7B2D8E;">The Process</h2>

<div class="bg-purple-50 p-6 rounded-lg mb-8">
  <ol class="space-y-4">
    <li class="flex items-start">
      <span class="font-bold mr-3 text-purple-700">1.</span>
      <div>
        <strong>Assessment</strong> — We examine the outer ear area to identify hair for removal.
      </div>
    </li>
    <li class="flex items-start">
      <span class="font-bold mr-3 text-purple-700">2.</span>
      <div>
        <strong>Cleansing</strong> — The area is cleaned to ensure proper wax adherence.
      </div>
    </li>
    <li class="flex items-start">
      <span class="font-bold mr-3 text-purple-700">3.</span>
      <div>
        <strong>Application</strong> — Warm wax is carefully applied to the outer ear only.
      </div>
    </li>
    <li class="flex items-start">
      <span class="font-bold mr-3 text-purple-700">4.</span>
      <div>
        <strong>Removal</strong> — Quick, precise removal for clean results.
      </div>
    </li>
  </ol>
</div>

<h2 class="text-2xl font-bold mb-4" style="color: #7B2D8E;">Safe and Professional</h2>

<div class="bg-gray-50 p-6 rounded-lg mb-8">
  <p class="mb-4">
    <strong>Important:</strong> We only wax the outer ear (the pinna). We never insert wax or any tools into the ear canal. This ensures your safety and comfort throughout the procedure.
  </p>
  <p>
    Our experienced estheticians use gentle techniques specifically designed for this sensitive area.
  </p>
</div>

<h2 class="text-2xl font-bold mb-4" style="color: #7B2D8E;">Book Your Ear Hair Waxing</h2>

<p class="text-lg">
  Quick, affordable, and effective. <a href="/bookingselection" style="color: #7B2D8E;" class="font-semibold hover:underline">Book your ear hair waxing appointment</a> at our Scottsdale location today! Only $15 for clean, polished results.
</p>

</ServicePage>